Try to fart!

02:12.966 --> 02:13.966
Trick...

02:13.968 --> 02:15.334
Or treat.

02:15.336 --> 02:17.903
Oh, ladies. I'm sorry, you just
got here during a bit of a...

02:17.905 --> 02:19.271
Ooh, I can see
your nipples, officer.

02:19.273 --> 02:23.375
Anything you see will
be held against you.

02:24.444 --> 02:26.078
And I'm harry potter.

02:26.080 --> 02:28.013
