03:30.411 --> 03:32.477
We're en route
with a 35-year-old male.

03:32.479 --> 03:35.380
Bp is 160/94, pulse is 108.

03:35.382 --> 03:37.749
And he's dressed
as zombie elvis, over!

03:39.018 --> 03:41.420
