feed him like a baby bird.

06:26.553 --> 06:29.888
How could that
possibly help?

06:29.890 --> 06:32.157
I'll tell you what
doesn't help-- that tone.

06:32.159 --> 06:33.925
Can we see him?

06:33.927 --> 06:35.360
Soon as he's
in recovery.

06:35.362 --> 06:36.728
Any other questions?

06:36.730 --> 06:38.363
Uh, no, we're just happy
that he's gonna be okay.

06:38.365 --> 06:39.364
