06:39.366 --> 06:40.599
My pleasure.

06:40.601 --> 06:42.667
By the way, <i>ferris bueller</i>
<i>is my favorite movie.</i>

06:45.371 --> 06:47.572
Wait, b-berta.
W-where are you going?

06:47.574 --> 06:48.707
We're not supposed
to go back there yet.

06:48.709 --> 06:50.542
I'm a nun at a hospital.

06:50.544 --> 06:52.911
I can do whatever
the hell I want.

06:59.585 --> 07:01.653
I'm dead.

07:05.958 --> 07:07.859
And I'm in hell.

07:08.961 --> 07:10.762
Relax.

07:10.764 --> 07:12.063
You're in the hospital.

07:12.065 --> 07:14.433
You had a mild heart attack,
but you're gonna be fine.

07:14.435 --> 07:16.201
I don't feel very good.

07:16.203 --> 07:18.437
That's because they put
a stent in your heart.

07:18.439 --> 07:20.772
But also I feel really good.

07:20.774 --> 07:25.043
That's because they put morphine
in your veins.

07:25.045 --> 07:27.746
We should start keeping morphine
in the house.

07:27.748 --> 07:30.582
I know a guy.

07:30.584 --> 07:33.985
Berta, you're so funny.

07:33.987 --> 07:37.222
I would've missed you so much
if I would've died.

07:37.224 --> 07:39.291
Oh, oh, but you don't
have to worry about that.

07:39.293 --> 07:40.392
Y-you're not going anywhere.

07:40.394 --> 07:41.960
I love you guys.

07:41.962 --> 07:43.261
We love you, too.

07:43.263 --> 07:45.597
You know, when I think about it,

07:45.599 --> 07:48.166
You guys are
my only real family.

07:48.168 --> 07:50.235
Oh, walden, that's so...

07:50.237 --> 07:52.604
Horrible.

07:52.606 --> 07:53.972
Okay.

07:53.974 --> 07:56.475
Saved your life, but whatever.

07:56.477 --> 07:58.610
My life is pathetic.

07:58.612 --> 08:01.680
I mean, thank you guys so much
for being here.

08:01.682 --> 08:04.516
But you're not good enough!

08:04.518 --> 08:07.252
Okay, now it sounds
like my family.

08:07.254 --> 08:09.020
Um...

08:09.022 --> 08:10.021
Maybe you should rest.

08:10.023 --> 08:11.590
You know, just go
to your happy place.

08:11.592 --> 08:12.991
