08:12.993 --> 08:13.992
Say when.

08:13.994 --> 08:15.460
Whe...

08:15.462 --> 08:17.863
(squeals)

08:17.865 --> 08:21.099
Dressed as a nun,
giving some guy morphine--

08:21.101 --> 08:23.735
Boy, does this take me
back to high school.

08:30.009 --> 08:32.344
Hey, how you feeling?

08:32.346 --> 08:33.445
I'm all right.

08:33.447 --> 08:35.313
Well, uh, I know

08:35.315 --> 08:37.616
Something that'll
make you feel better.

08:37.618 --> 08:39.784
I made some of my famous
three bean salad.

08:40.820 --> 08:42.220
The secret--

08:42.222 --> 08:44.256
(whispers):
I use four beans.

08:45.825 --> 08:48.126
Garbanzo.

08:48.128 --> 08:49.694
Shh.

08:49.696 --> 08:52.163
You ever look out at the ocean

08:52.165 --> 08:54.466
And think about how small
and insignificant you are?

08:54.468 --> 08:57.836
I don't need the ocean;
I can just call my mother.

08:57.838 --> 08:59.471
I almost died, alan.

08:59.473 --> 09:01.072
But the important thing is
you didn't.

09:01.074 --> 09:03.174
So, now you just have
to listen to your doctors,

09:03.176 --> 09:04.543
Don't stress about anything
and relax.

09:04.545 --> 09:06.978
(shrill laughing)
(screams)

09:06.980 --> 09:09.147
Sorry, sorry, sorry.

09:11.751 --> 09:13.818
Sorry.

09:13.820 --> 09:15.887
That was supposed to scare the
life out of trick-or-treaters,

09:15.889 --> 09:16.988
Not you.

09:16.990 --> 09:18.089
This sucks!

09:18.091 --> 09:20.425
How am I the one
with a stent in my heart?

09:20.427 --> 09:22.260
I'm healthy, I-I'm fit.

09:22.262 --> 09:24.095
You sit in front
of the tv every night,

09:24.097 --> 09:26.097
Shoveling a pint of ice cream
down your throat.

09:26.099 --> 09:27.699
Hey, I eat my feelings,

09:27.701 --> 09:29.935
