what's difficult?

11:22.949 --> 11:25.684
Removing a marble
your kid shoved up his nose.

11:25.686 --> 11:26.818
I did something like that.

11:26.820 --> 11:28.286
I jammed a penny up there.

11:28.288 --> 11:30.955
I was trying to get a gumball
to fall out of my butt.

11:30.957 --> 11:32.891
But a kid
is permanent.

11:32.893 --> 11:34.359
It's not like you're dating.

11:34.361 --> 11:36.661
You can't just stop calling
or change your number

11:36.663 --> 11:38.797
Or fake your own death
because they annoy you.

11:38.799 --> 11:40.131
You do that to women?

11:40.133 --> 11:41.433
No, they do it to me.

11:43.302 --> 11:46.037
Look, I-I'm sorry if it feels
like I'm being negative,

11:46.039 --> 11:48.306
Because the truth is,
you know, kids are amazing.

11:48.308 --> 11:50.575
But you just had
this big health scare,

11:50.577 --> 11:52.510
And you're probably not
in the best frame of mind

11:52.512 --> 11:53.912
To make life decisions.

11:53.914 --> 11:56.848
I mean, this morning,
you cried at a beer commercial.

11:56.850 --> 12:00.385
Yeah, but the horse and
the puppy were best friends!

12:00.387 --> 12:02.053
Look,

12:02.055 --> 12:03.922
Having a heart attack
didn't make me realize

12:03.924 --> 12:06.491
I want to have a kid,
it made me realize

12:06.493 --> 12:08.059
I don't want to live
another day without one.

12:08.061 --> 12:10.028
It was like a wake-up call.

12:10.030 --> 12:11.362
All right.

12:11.364 --> 12:15.500
If you really want to do this,
I will be here to support you.

12:15.502 --> 12:16.901
From my room.

12:16.903 --> 12:20.238
Which, fyi, is way too drafty
to use as a nursery.

12:20.240 --> 12:22.507
Don't worry.
You're not going anywhere.

12:22.509 --> 12:23.908
Sweet! Let's get that kid!

12:24.744 --> 12:25.944
So, uh, who's the lucky lady

12:25.946 --> 12:27.879
Who's gonna receive your seed?

12:27.881 --> 12:30.215
See, you just put
your creepy little finger

12:30.217 --> 12:31.483
Right on the problem.

12:32.952 --> 12:35.253
I haven't exactly been
successful in love.

12:35.255 --> 12:39.290
It's like I'm running javascript
and women are running html5.

12:40.893 --> 12:43.428
Talking like that is part
of the problem, isn't it?

